# =============================================================================
# Cursor / AI 索引忽略（与 .codexignore、.codex/config.toml 同步）
# 改表流程：xiuxian配置表/indir/*.xlsx → export_excel_json.bat → data/exportjson/
# =============================================================================

# --- Godot 编辑器缓存与 headless/CI 测试临时目录 ---
.godot/
.godot_test_*/

# --- Excel 配置源与 inspect 中间产物 ---
xiuxian配置表/indir/
xiuxian配置表/**/previews/
**/*.xlsx
**/*.inspect.ndjson

# --- 配置表导出工具本地输出（previews / 副本 xlsx / inspect）---
outputs/

# --- Godot 自动生成 sidecar（.gd/.tscn 才是源码）---
**/*.import
**/*.uid
**/*.translation

# --- 二进制美术与音频（路径引用在 .tscn/.gd；AI 无需读像素/波形）---
assets/**/*.png
assets/**/*.jpg
assets/**/*.jpeg
assets/**/*.webp
assets/**/*.gif
assets/**/*.ttf
assets/**/*.otf
assets/**/*.woff
assets/**/*.woff2
**/*.wav

# --- docs 设计稿大图 ---
docs/**/*.png

# --- 系统/编辑器杂项 ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.tmp
*.bak
